{"tid":563980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"波音造飛機要多久？CEO發豪語：只要10小時","createTime":"2018-02-17T13:02:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T18:24:21.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f348f41d4675d3e619a9137d862fb8a47a491054","tid":563980,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:02:59.000Z","msg":"波音執行長米倫巴格（Dennis Muilenburg）周四接受美國財經媒體CNBC訪問時表示，2020年前波音將達到每年生產逾900架飛機的目標，相當於每不到10小時生產1架。<br />\n<br />\n波銀去年商用飛機交機量為763架，創史上最高紀錄，相當於每11.5小時生產1架新飛機。波銀今年將朝2020年的崇高目標再邁進一步，該公司今年交機量估為810至815架。<br />\n<br />\n米倫巴格說：「我們預期航空流量和乘客流量將以每年約6%至7%的速度成長，這將是全球飛機業成長的動力。」米倫巴格預測，未來20年全球機隊規模將成長1倍，全球將需要4.1萬架新飛機。（林文彬／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.finance.appledaily.com/realtime/20180217/1299769/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.finance.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20180217%2F1299769%2F&d=u16ti%2BQKRfEP63qtE5Xr1NtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=a2bb4602\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.finance.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20180217%2F1299769%2F&h=2ffce3d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.finance.appledaily.com/realtime/20180217/1299769/</a>"},{"pid":"e66aced6dbf58baeba2904a99d6de98bb81a6301","tid":563980,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":19,"score":-17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:05:42.000Z","msg":"所謂10個鐘只係喺度砌返好咋咩<br />\n唔通真係由0開始咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋個engine都唔係Boeing整架啦, 係Rolls Royce"},{"pid":"dfce12a0b411ff0ca0e67d7c5bc71b34e8ae37eb","tid":563980,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:06:44.000Z","msg":"平均10個鐘有一架出廠"},{"pid":"df0b5370c74363a5747aa7672acc4e5c017d76e7","tid":563980,"uid":44454,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"e66aced6dbf58baeba2904a99d6de98bb81a6301","tid":563980,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":19,"score":-17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:05:42.000Z","msg":"所謂10個